</td></tr> <tr><td align="center"><table width="60%" border="1"><tr align="center"><th></th><th><font face="calibri" size="4" color="#A4A4A4">Vehiculo mejor rendimiento semanal</font></th><th><font face="calibri" size="4" color="#A4A4A4">Vehiculo peor rendimiento semanal</font></th></tr><tr align="center"><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">Patente o VIN</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">K-192</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4"> K234</font></td></tr><tr align="center"><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">Km/Lts</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">2.3</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">0.2</font></td></tr></tr><tr align="center"><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">Dia</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">Domingo 18/03/2018</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">Jueves 15/03/2018</font></td></tr></table></td></tr> <tr><td align="center"><img src="https://charturl.com/i/pt-0Wvx/semana?d=%7B%0A%22options%22+%3A+%7B%0A%22data%22+%3A+%7B%0A%22labels%22+%3A+%5B%0A++++++++%22L%22%2C%0A++++++++%22M%22%2C%0A++++++++%22M%22%2C%0A++++++++%22J%22%2C%0A++++++++%22V%22%2C%0A++++++++%22S%22%2C%0A++++++++%22D%22%0A%5D%2C%0A%22datasets%22+%3A+%5B%0A%7B%0A%22label%22+%3A+%22Vehiculo+Mejor+Rendimiento%22%2C%0A%22backgroundColor%22+%3A+%22rgba%2890%2C90%2C90%2C0.5%29%22%2C%0A%22data%22+%3A+%5B%0A2.3%2C0%2C2.2%2C2.1%2C0%2C0%2C2.3%5D%0A%7D%2C%0A%7B%0A%22label%22+%3A+%22Vehiculo+Peor+Rendimiento%22%2C%0A%22backgroundColor%22+%3A+%22rgba%28220%2C220%2C220%2C0.5%29%22%2C%0A%22data%22+%3A+%5B%0A0%2C0%2C0.4%2C0.2%2C0%2C0%2C0%5D%0A%7D%0A%5D%0A%7D%0A%7D%0A%7D&s=UilOiC4iGdDTuDzfdme7buo5tXCE3b8FQW%2BZjznLnJI%3D" width="400" height="250">
</td></tr><tr><td align="center"><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#2E64FE">RECOMENDACION:Manten el inflado de tus neumaticos con la presion adecuada, puedes reducir el consumo de combustible hasta en un 3%.</font><br><br></td></tr><tr><td  align="center"><font face="calibri" size="4" color="#A4A4A4">Comparado a la semana anterior</font><br>

</td></tr> <tr><td align="center"><table width="60%" border="1"><tr align="center"><th></th><th><font face="calibri" size="4" color="#A4A4A4">Vehiculo mejor rendimiento semanal</font></th><th><font face="calibri" size="4" color="#A4A4A4">Vehiculo peor rendimiento semanal</font></th></tr><tr align="center"><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">Patente o VIN</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">TKTC0035</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">TKTC0036</font></td></tr><tr align="center"><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">Km/Lts</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">4.9</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">0.5</font></td></tr></tr><tr align="center"><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">Dia</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">Jueves 15/03/2018</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">Lunes 19/03/2018</font></td></tr></table></td></tr> <tr><td align="center"><img src="https://charturl.com/i/pt-0Wvx/semana?d=%7B%0A%22options%22+%3A+%7B%0A%22data%22+%3A+%7B%0A%22labels%22+%3A+%5B%0A++++++++%22L%22%2C%0A++++++++%22M%22%2C%0A++++++++%22M%22%2C%0A++++++++%22J%22%2C%0A++++++++%22V%22%2C%0A++++++++%22S%22%2C%0A++++++++%22D%22%0A%5D%2C%0A%22datasets%22+%3A+%5B%0A%7B%0A%22label%22+%3A+%22Vehiculo+Mejor+Rendimiento%22%2C%0A%22backgroundColor%22+%3A+%22rgba%2890%2C90%2C90%2C0.5%29%22%2C%0A%22data%22+%3A+%5B%0A0%2C0%2C0%2C4.9%2C0%2C0%2C0%5D%0A%7D%2C%0A%7B%0A%22label%22+%3A+%22Vehiculo+Peor+Rendimiento%22%2C%0A%22backgroundColor%22+%3A+%22rgba%28220%2C220%2C220%2C0.5%29%22%2C%0A%22data%22+%3A+%5B%0A0.5%2C0%2C0.8%2C1.1%2C0.9%2C0.9%2C0.8%5D%0A%7D%0A%5D%0A%7D%0A%7D%0A%7D&s=WEYqDKk%2By1SmW%2FUOS8ml5uhVXFiO4QJqqEhtxKYpIcY%3D" width="400" height="250">

</td></tr> <tr><td align="center"><table width="60%" border="1"><tr align="center"><th></th><th><font face="calibri" size="4" color="#A4A4A4">Vehiculo mejor rendimiento semanal</font></th><th><font face="calibri" size="4" color="#A4A4A4">Vehiculo peor rendimiento semanal</font></th></tr><tr align="center"><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">Patente o VIN</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">GDRP24</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">DWTF27</font></td></tr><tr align="center"><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">Km/Lts</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">1.3</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">0.4</font></td></tr></tr><tr align="center"><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">Dia</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">Viernes 16/03/2018</font></td><td><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#A4A4A4">Domingo 18/03/2018</font></td></tr></table></td></tr> <tr><td align="center"><img src="https://charturl.com/i/pt-0Wvx/semana?d=%7B%0A%22options%22+%3A+%7B%0A%22data%22+%3A+%7B%0A%22labels%22+%3A+%5B%0A++++++++%22L%22%2C%0A++++++++%22M%22%2C%0A++++++++%22M%22%2C%0A++++++++%22J%22%2C%0A++++++++%22V%22%2C%0A++++++++%22S%22%2C%0A++++++++%22D%22%0A%5D%2C%0A%22datasets%22+%3A+%5B%0A%7B%0A%22label%22+%3A+%22Vehiculo+Mejor+Rendimiento%22%2C%0A%22backgroundColor%22+%3A+%22rgba%2890%2C90%2C90%2C0.5%29%22%2C%0A%22data%22+%3A+%5B%0A0%2C0%2C1.0%2C0%2C1.3%2C0%2C0%5D%0A%7D%2C%0A%7B%0A%22label%22+%3A+%22Vehiculo+Peor+Rendimiento%22%2C%0A%22backgroundColor%22+%3A+%22rgba%28220%2C220%2C220%2C0.5%29%22%2C%0A%22data%22+%3A+%5B%0A0%2C0%2C0.8%2C0.8%2C0.6%2C1.0%2C0.4%5D%0A%7D%0A%5D%0A%7D%0A%7D%0A%7D&s=uKKZiaJqv9S6NzScbItCh3dL1PaMHLu8F3Orsp2SFcU%3D" width="400" height="250">
</td></tr><tr><td align="center"><font size="2" face="calibri" color="#2E64FE">RECOMENDACION:Manten el inflado de tus neumaticos con la presion adecuada, puedes reducir el consumo de combustible hasta en un 3%.</font><br><br></td></tr><tr><td  align="center"><font face="calibri" size="4" color="#A4A4A4">Comparado a la semana anterior</font><br>
